0the%20US%2C%20and%20prohibit%20US%20foreign%20assistance%20and%20arms%20sales%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Congressional%20Research%20Service%20(CRS).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThousands%20of%20people%20and%20companies%2C%20both%20Iranian%20and%20foreign%2C%20have%20been%20targeted%20under%20the%20sanctions%20program%20as%20Washington%20has%20sought%20to%20constrain%20Iran's%20government%20and%20change%20its%20behavior%2C%20the%20CRS%20said%20in%20a%20report%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fexplained-what-options-does-israel-have-to-strike-back-at-iran-5455454%5C%22%3EExplained%3A%20What%20Options%20Does%20Israel%20Have%20To%20Strike%20Back%20At%20Iran%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20concerns%20have%20included%20Iran's%20nuclear%20program%2C%20human%20rights%20abuses%2C%20and%20its%20support%20for%20groups%20the%20US%20sees%20as%20terrorists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUS%20sanctions%20on%20Iran%20are%20arguably%20the%20most%20extensive%20and%20comprehensive%20set%20of%20sanctions%20that%20the%20United%20States%20maintains%20on%20any%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CRS%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20more%20can%20the%20US%20do%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeter%20Harrell%2C%20a%20former%20National%20Security%20Council%20official%2C%20said%20US%20options%20for%20further%20sanctions%20include%20targeting%20the%20flow%20of%20Iranian%20oil%20and%20playing%20a%20more%20aggressive%20game%20of%20%26quot%3BWhac-A-Mole%26quot%3B%20to%20go%20after%20Iran's%20front%20companies%20and%20financiers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20significant%20moves%20would%20be%20for%20Washington%20to%20get%20the%20European%20Union%20and%20other%20Western%20allies%20to%20impose%20multilateral%20sanctions%20on%20Tehran%2C%20he%20said%2C%20as%20most%20of%20the%20sanctions%20in%20place%20against%20Iran%20currently%20are%20US%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20reinstated%20US%20sanctions%20that%20were%20eased%20under%20an%20international%20deal%20on%20Tehran's%20nuclear%20program%20when%20he%20withdrew%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20be%20realistic%20that%20from%20a%20US%20perspective%2C%20while%20there%20are%20always%20more%20sanctions%20you%20can%20impose%2C%20we%20are%20in%20a%20world%20of%20diminishing%20actual%20economic%20pressure%20because%20we%20have%20so%20many%20sanctions%20already%20in%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20Harrell%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20Congress%20considering%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHouse%20Republican%20leaders%20have%20accused%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20of%20failing%20to%20enforce%20existing%20measures%20and%20said%20they%20would%20take%20up%20a%20series%20of%20bills%20to%20sharpen%20sanctions%20on%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20them%20is%20legislation%20that%20would%20increase%20congressional%20oversight%20of%20sanctions%20waivers%2C%20tighten%20restrictions%20on%20the%20export%20of%20US%20goods%20and%20technology%20to%20Iran%2C%20and%20require%20the%20administration%20to%20ensure%20humanitarian%20exemptions%20to%20the%20sanctions%20do%20not%20facilitate%20acts%20of%20terrorism%20or%20the%20proliferation%20of%20weapons%20of%20mass%20destruction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWatch%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fviral-video-david-camerons-double-standards-over-iran-israel-conflict-5446298%5C%22%3EViral%20Video%3A%20David%20Cameron's%20%26quot%3BDouble%20Standards%26quot%3B%20Over%20Iran-Israel%20Conflict%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20immediate%20indication%20of%20when%2C%20if%20ever%2C%20any%20of%20the%20measures%20would%20become%20law%2C%20which%20would%20require%20passage%20by%20the%20Democratic-led%20Senate%20and%20the%20signature%20of%20Democratic%20President%20Joe%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20House%20late%20on%20Monday%20overwhelmingly%20passed%20a%20bill%20called%20the%20Iran-China%20Energy%20Sanctions%20Act%2C%20which%20would%20expand%20sanctions%20on%20Iran%20by%20requiring%20annual%20reports%20to%20determine%20whether%20Chinese%20financial%20institutions%20have%20participated%20in%20transactions%20on%20Iranian%20oil.%20It%20would%20ban%20US%20financial%20institutions%20from%20having%20accounts%20for%20any%20Chinese%20entities%20that%20engage%20in%20those%20deals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20faces%20an%20uncertain%20future%20in%20the%20Senate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Democratic-led%20Senate%20may%20consider%20its%20own%20legislation.%20The%20Senate%20Foreign%20Relations%20Committee%20passed%20a%20bill%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20would%20impose%20measures%20on%20foreign%20ports%20and%20refineries%20that%20process%20oil%20exported%20from%20Iran%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20US%20sanctions%20after%20a%20companion%20bill%20passed%20last%20year%20in%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Biden%20administration%20has%20imposed%20sanctions%20on%20hundreds%20of%20people%20and%20entities%20in%20Iran-related%20action%20since%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20are%20the%20key%20parts%20of%20the%20current%20measures%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20sanctions%20on%20Iran%20have%20targeted%20its%20nuclear%20capabilities%2C%20energy%20and%20defense%20sectors%2C%20government%20officials%2C%20banks%2C%20and%20other%20aspects%20of%20Iran's%20economy%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20US%20has%20imposed%20sanctions%20on%20the%20Atomic%20EnergyOrganization%20of%20Iran%20and%20other%20companies%20it%20says%20are%20linked%20to%20Iran's%20nuclear%20program%2C%20as%20well%20as%20dozens%20of%20banks%2C%20includingthe%20Central%20Bank%20of%20Iran.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWashington%20has%20also%20targeted%20the%20National%20Iranian%20Oil%20Company%2C%20Ministry%20of%20Petroleum%2C%20and%20others%20to%20stem%20revenue%20Iran%20receives%20from%20its%20energy%20sector%2C%20and%20has%20targeted%20comp