A%22Noida%20Woman%20Who%20Quit%20Corporate%20Job%20Makes%20It%20To%20UPSC%20Top%2020%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%C2%A0Noida%20resident%20Wardah%20Khan%2C%20who%20quit%20her%20corporate%20job%20to%20prepare%20for%20civil%20services%2C%20secured%20the%2018th%20rank%20in%20the%20UPSC%20exam%202023%20in%20the%20prestigious%20test%2C%20results%20of%20which%20were%20announced%20on%20Tuesday%20by%20the%20UPSC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2024-year-old%20UPSC%20qualifier%20says%20she%20has%20opted%20for%20the%20Indian%20Foreign%20Service%20(IFS)%20as%20her%20first%20preference%20and%20wishes%20to%20make%20the%20country%20proud%20at%20global%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLike%20every%20other%20aspirant%2C%20when%20we%20start%20our%20journey%20we%20dream%20of%20finding%20our%20name%20on%20the%20result%20list.%20But%20getting%20into%20the%20top%2020%20was%20unimaginable%2C%20I%20had%20not%20imagined%20to%20be%20able%20to%20be%20in%20the%20top%2020.%20It's%20a%20dreamy%20feeling%20right%20now.%20Everybody%20in%20my%20family%20is%20very%20happy%20and%20beaming%20with%20pride%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Khan%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20opted%20for%20Indian%20Foreign%20Service%20(IFS)%20as%20my%20first%20preference%2C%20so%20I%20would%20like%20to%20further%20the%20image%20of%20India%20across%20global%20platforms%20and%20multilateral%20institutions%20and%20help%20our%20Indian%20diaspora%20abroad%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20%7C%20Noida%20resident%20Wardah%20Khan%20secures%2018th%20rank%20in%20UPSC%202023.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnShe%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20never%20thought%20that%20I%20would%20make%20it%20to%20Top%2020.%20I%20just%20wanted%20to%20make%20it%20to%20the%20list%20(of%20qualifiers).%20This%20is%20a%20huge%20moment%20for%20my%20family%20and%20me.%20This%20was%20my%20second%20attempt.%20I%20have%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F2KoPdlDPmV%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F2KoPdlDPmV%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1780238559028380156%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%2016%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20resident%20of%20Vivek%20Vihar%20in%20Noida's%20Sector%2082%2C%20Ms%20Khan%20pursued%20her%20Bachelors%20in%20Commerce%20(Honours)%20from%20the%20Khalsa%20College%20of%20Delhi%20University.%20The%20only%20child%20of%20her%20parents%2C%20she%20lives%20with%20her%20mother.%20Her%20father%20passed%20away%20nine%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20how%20she%20got%20inclined%20towards%20UPSC%2C%20Ms%20Khan%20said%20that%20during%20her%20college%20days%2C%20she%20always%20had%20an%20interest%20in%20geopolitics%2C%20in%20subjects%20such%20as%20history%20and%20polity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20used%20to%20participate%20in%20debates%20and%20MUNs%20(mock%20United%20Nations)%20during%20her%20college%20days%20but%20even%20then%20the%20idea%20of%20taking%20up%20civil%20services%20as%20a%20career%20path%20had%20not%20come%20to%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20during%20her%20job%20tenure%20that%20Ms%20Khan%20realised%20she%20wanted%20to%20become%20a%20civil%20servant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20worked%20for%20a%20corporate%20firm%20for%20eight%20months.%20That%20didn't%20sort%20of%20satisfy%20me.%20I%20wanted%20to%20give%20back%20to%20the%20society%20and%20wanted%20to%20work%20for%20my%20country%20and%20transform%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20realised%20the%20kind%20of%20syllabus%20and%20opportunities%20that%20this%20career%20(civil%20services)%20offers%20aligns%20with%20my%20interest%20and%20hence%20I%20decided%20to%20pursue%20it%20and%20quit%20my%20job%20in%20eight%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20prepared%20at%20home%20but%20also%20took%20online%20coaching%20from%20a%20private%20institution%20for%20one%20complete%20year%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20tips%20for%20UPSC%20aspirants%2C%20the%20AIR%2018-holder%20said%20there%20are%20a%20few%20postulates%20that%20every%20candidate%20should%20keep%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirst%20and%20foremost%2C%20you%20have%20to%20be%20very%20thorough%20with%20the%20basics%20like%20NCERT%20and%20Polity%20by%20Laxmikant.%20These%20are%20the%20basic%20books%20that%20you%20have%20to%20be%20thorough%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20also%20must%20have%20made%20proper%20syllabus%20heads%20of%20your%20mains%20and%20your%20optional%20should%20also%20be%20prepared%20with%20notes%20before%20the%20cycle%20communities.%20These%20are%20some%20of%20the%20things%20that%20must%20be%20kept%20in%20mind%2C%26quot%3B%20Khan%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%201%2C016%20candidates%20--%20664%20men%20and%20352%20women%20--%20have%20qualified%20in%20the%20examination%20and%20have%20been%20recommended%20by%20the%20Union%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20(UPSC)%20for%20appointment%20to%20various%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAditya%20Srivastava%2C%20a%20trainee%20Indian%20Police%20Service%20officer%2C%20has%20topped%20the%20civil%20services%20examination%202023%2C%20results%20of%20which%20were%20announced%20on%20Tuesday%20by%20the%20Union%20Public%20Service%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnimesh%20Pradhan%2C%20Donuru%20Ananya%20Reddy%2C%20P%20K%20Sidharth%20Ramkumar%20and%20Ruhani%20have%20secured%20second%2C%20third%2C%20fourth%20and%20fifth%20rank%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%