ld%20be%20the%20first%20Ram%20Navami%20since%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20idol%20at%20the%20new%20temple%2C%20inaugurated%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20January%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20system%20was%20tested%20by%20the%20scientists%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20basic%20objective%20of%20the%20Surya%20Tilak%20project%20is%20to%20focus%20a%20'tilak'%20on%20the%20forehead%20of%20Shri%20Ram%20idol%20on%20every%20Shri%20Ram%20Navami%20day.%20Under%20the%20project%2C%20sunlight%20will%20be%20brought%20on%20the%20forehead%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20at%20noon%20on%20Shri%20Ram%20Navami%20in%20the%20Chaitra%20month%20every%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20S%20K%20Panigrahi%2C%20scientist%20at%20CSIR-CBRI%20Roorkee%2C%20who%20was%20associated%20with%20the%20project%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20further%2C%20Dr%20S%20K%20Panigrahi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20position%20of%20the%20Sun%20changes%20every%20year%20on%20the%20day%20of%20Shri%20Ram%20Navami.%20Detailed%20calculations%20show%20that%20the%20date%20of%20Shri%20Ram%20Navami%20repeats%20every%2019%20years.%26quot%3B%20According%20to%20a%20senior%20scientist%20of%20Council%20of%20Scientific%20and%20Industrial%20Research%20(CSIR)-Central%20Building%20Research%20Institute%20(CBRI)%2C%20Roorkee%2C%20the%20planned%20tilak%20size%20is%2058%20mm.%20The%20exact%20period%20of%20tilak%20on%20the%20forehead%20centre%20is%20about%20three%20to%20three-and-a-half%20minutes%2C%20with%20two%20minutes%20of%20full%20illumination%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20member%20of%20Shri%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20Teerth%20Kshetra%20Trust%2C%20Anil%20Mishra%2C%20told%20PTI%2C%20%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20Surya%20tilak%2C%20devotees%20will%20be%20allowed%20inside%20the%20Ram%20temple.%20Around%20100%20LEDs%20are%20being%20put%20up%20by%20the%20temple%20trust%2C%20and%2050%20by%20the%20government%2C%20which%20will%20show%20the%20Ram%20Navami%20celebrations.%20People%20will%20be%20able%20to%20see%20the%20celebrations%20from%20where%20they%20are%20present.%26quot%3B%20Sharing%20his%20personal%20experience%20in%20installing%20this%20unique%20mechanism%2C%20Dr%20D%20P%20Kanungo%2C%20chief%20scientist%20at%20CSIR-CBRI%2C%20Roorkee%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BActually%20this%20is%20meticulously%20planned%2C%20designed%20and%20implemented%20to%20achieve%20utmost%20accuracy.%26quot%3B%20This%20will%20be%20a%20testament%20to%20our%20scientific%20acumen%20and%20indigenous%20technological%20development%20to%20showcase%20before%20our%20countrymen%20who%20have%20all%20the%20faith%20in%20and%20support%20to%20our%20scientific%20community%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20what%20will%20happen%20to%20Surya%20tilak%20in%20case%20of%20a%20cloudy%20sky%2C%20Kanungo%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThat's%20the%20limitation.%20We%20don't%20wish%20to%20do%20with%20artificial%20light%20because%20of%20the%20faith%20and%20belief%20of%20our%20people.%26quot%3B%20In%20consultation%20with%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Astrophysics%20(IIA)%2C%20Bangalore%2C%20the%20CSIR-CBRI%2C%20Roorkee%20team%20has%20developed%20a%20mechanism%20for%20a%2019-year%20period%20to%20steer%20the%20sunlight%20from%20the%20third%20floor%20of%20the%20temple%20to%20the%20'garbha%20griha'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20detailed%20complete%20design%20to%20bring%20the%20sunlight%20to%20the%20garbha%20griha%20is%20developed%20by%20CBRI%2C%20with%20the%20IIA%20providing%20consultancy%20for%20the%20optical%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fabrication%20of%20optical%20elements%2C%20pipes%2C%20tilt%20mechanism%20and%20other%20related%20components%20are%20carried%20out%20by%20Optics%20and%20Allied%20Engg%20Pvt%20Ltd%20(Optica)%2C%20a%20Bangalore-based%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20implementing%20the%20opto-mechanical%20system%20in%20the%20Ram%20temple%20for%20Surya%20tilak%2C%20a%20scaled%20down%20model%20suitable%20for%20the%20Roorkee%20locality%20has%20been%20successfully%20validated.%20A%20full%20scale%20model%20has%20been%20successfully%20validated%20at%20Optica%20site%20at%20Bangalore%20in%20March%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CSIR-CBRI%2C%20Roorkee%20team%20along%20with%20IIA%20Bangalore%20and%20Optica%20Bangalore%20completed%20the%20installation%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20April%2C%20and%20repeated%20trials%20have%20been%20done%2C%20Dr%20S%20K%20Panigrahi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20explaining%20the%20opto-mechanical%20system%20for%20Surya%20tilak%2C%20Dr%20S%20K%20Panigrahi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20opto-mechanical%20system%20consists%20of%20four%20mirrors%20and%20four%20lenses%20fitted%20inside%20the%20tilt%20mechanism%20and%20piping%20systems.%20The%20complete%20cover%20with%20aperture%20for%20the%20tilt%20mechanism%20is%20placed%20at%20the%20top%20floor%20to%20divert%20the%20Sun%20rays%20through%20mirrors%20and%20lenses%20to%20the%20garbha%20girha.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThe%20final%20lens%20and%20mirror%20focus%20the%20Sun%20rays%20to%20the%20forehead%20of%20Shri%20Ram%20facing%20towards%20the%20east.%20The%20tilt%20mechanism%20is%20used%20to%20adjust%20the%20first%20mirror%20tilting%20for%20sending%20the%20Sun%20rays%20towards%20the%20north%20direction%20to%20the%20second%20mirror%20for%20making%20the%20Surya%20tilak%20every%20year%20on%20Shri%20Ram%20Navami%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20piping%20and%20other%20parts%20are%20manufactured%20using%20the%20brass%20material.%20The%20mirrors%20and%20lenses%20which%20are%20used%20are%20of%20very%20high%20quality%20and%20durable%20to%20sustain%20for%20a%20long%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20inner%20surface%20of%20pipes%2C%20elbows%20and%20enclosures%20are%20black%20powder%20coated%20to%20avoid%20scattering%20of%20sunlight.%20Also%20at%20the%20top%20aperture%2C%20IR%20(infra%20red)%20filter%20glass%20is%20used%20to%20restrict%20the%20Sun%20heat%20wave%20to%20fall%20on%20the%20forehead%20of%20the%20idol%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20S%20K%20Panigrahi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20team%20from%20CSIR-CBRI%20Roorkee%20includes%20Dr%20S%20K%20Panigrahi%2C%20Dr%20R%20S%20Bisht%2C%20Kanti%20Solanki%2C%20V%20Chakradhar%2C%20Dinesh%20and%20Sameer.%20Prof%20R%20Pradeep%20Kumar%20(Director%2C%20CSIR-CBRI)%20mentored%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20IIA%20Bangalore%20side%2C%20Dr%20Anna%20Purni%20S%20(Director%20IIA)%2C%20Er%20S%20Sriram%20and%20Professor%20Tushar%20Prabhu%20are%20the%20consultants.%20Rajinder%20Kotaria%2C%20managing%20director%2C%20Optica%2C%20and%20his%20team%20Nagraj%2C%20Vivek%2C%20Thava%20Kumar%20were%20actively%20involved%20in%20fabrication%20and%20installation%20part.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713294480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fhagk5s18_ram-lalla-holi-_625x300_25_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fayodhya-temple-all-set-for-surya-tilak-of-ram-lalla-on-ram-navami-5457775%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20noon%20on%20Ram%20Navami%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20Sun's%20rays%20will%20fall%20on%20the%20forehead%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20a%20'Surya%20tilak'%20of%20the%20deity%20made%20possible%20by%20an%20elaborate%20mechanism%20involving%20mirrors%20and%20lenses.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fayodhya-temple-all-set-for-surya-tilak-of-ram-lalla-on-ram-navami-5457775%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fayodhya-temple-all-set-for-surya-tilak-of-ram-lalla-on-ram-navami-5457775%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fayodhya-temple-all-set-for-surya-tilak-of-ram-lalla-on-ram