ar%20whether%20the%20woman%20has%20paid%20the%20fine%20and%20settled%20the%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%20December%202023%2C%20a%20man%20in%20Bengaluru%20was%20served%20a%20notice%20by%20the%20traffic%20police%20to%20clear%20dues%20worth%20Rs%201.34%20lakh%20generated%20by%20his%20255%20traffic%20violations.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20in%20Deccan%20Herald%2C%20the%20man%20named%20Elumalai%20had%20accumulated%20the%20violations%20over%20a%20period%20of%20two%20years.%20His%20details%20came%20up%20when%20the%20Traffic%20management%20Centre%20(TMC)%20was%20looking%20for%20vehicles%20with%20a%20high%20number%20of%20traffic%20violations.%20The%20information%20was%20sent%20to%20police%20stations%20across%20the%20city.%20The%20traffic%20police%20personnel%20were%20asked%20to%20track%20down%20such%20vehicles%20and%20recover%20fines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20then%20started%20their%20investigation%20and%20found%20that%20a%20scooter%20registered%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Elumalai%2C%20a%20daily%20wager%2C%20had%20255%20traffic%20violations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20called%20to%20the%20police%20station%20and%20told%20about%20it.%20Elumalai%20told%20the%20police%20personnel%20that%20he%20was%20unaware%20of%20the%20intelligent%20traffic%20management%20system%20(ITMS)%20cameras%20installed%20across%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Deccan%20Herald%20report%20said%20that%20Elumalai%20paid%20Rs%2010%2C000%20as%20spot%20fine%20and%20settled%2020%20cases.%20The%20police%20impounded%20his%20Suzuki%20Access%20scooter%2C%20the%20outlet%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713285720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2F2qpbloeg_traffic-light-large_625x300_30_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Fbengaluru-woman-fined-rs-1-36-lakhs-for-violating-traffic-rules-270-times-report-5456869%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20woman%20was%20seen%20tripling%20on%20a%20scoo