To%20Look%20At%20Amul%20Babies%3F%26quot%3B%20Himanta%20Sarma's%20Jibe%20At%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHours%20after%20Congress%20leader%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20led%20a%20roadshow%20in%20Assam's%20Jorhat%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20claimed%20that%20an%20%26quot%3Binsignificant%26quot%3B%20number%20of%20people%20attended%20it%20and%20that%20watching%20rhinos%20at%20the%20Kaziranga%20National%20Park%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bmore%20beneficial%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20heard%20around%202%2C000-3%2C000%20people%20gathered%20(at%20Priyanka%20Vadra's%20roadshow).%20It%20was%20not%20significant.%20Who%20will%20come%20to%20see%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%3F%20People%20will%20rather%20visit%20Kaziranga%20and%20watch%20tigers%2C%20rhinos%2C%20and%20the%20time%20spent%20there%20will%20be%20more%20useful%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20was%20speaking%20to%20reporters%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20an%20election%20campaign%20in%20Majuli.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMembers%20of%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20are%20only%20fit%20for%20advertising%20campaigns%2C%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat's%20the%20benefit%20of%20seeing%20the%20Gandhi%20family%3F%20They%20look%20fit%20for%20the%20Amul%20campaign%2C%20so%20they%20are%20Amul%20babies.%20It's%20more%20beneficial%20to%20watch%20rhinos%20at%20Kaziranga%20than%20catching%20a%20glimpse%20of%20Amul%20babies%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeading%20a%20massive%202-km%20long%20roadshow%20in%20support%20of%20Congress%20candidate%20Gaurav%20Gogoi%20earlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20Ms%20Vadra%20said%20the%20daily%20wages%20of%20tea%20garden%20workers%20will%20be%20hiked%20if%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20wins%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20Gaurav%20Gogoi's%20poll%20prospects%2C%20Mr%20Sarma%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSome%20people%20want%20to%20say%20that%20Gaurav%20Gogoi%20was%20an%20active%20parliamentarian.%20I%20challenge%20anyone%20who%20can%20show%20me%20a%20single%20word%20spoken%20by%20him%20for%20the%20Kaliabor%20constituency.%20Has%20he%20spoken%20a%20single%20word%20for%20Jorhat%2C%20Majuli%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gogoi%20is%20a%20sitting%20Congress%20MP%20from%20Kaliabor%2C%20which%20was%20rechristened%20Kaziranga%20after%20delimitation%20last%20year.%20This%20time%20he%20is%20contesting%20from%20Jorhat%20and%20looking%20for%20a%20third%20consecutive%20term%20in%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20need%20an%20active%20parliamentarian%20to%20shout%20'Rahul%20Gandhi%20%3Cem%3Ezindabad%3C%2Fem%3E'.%20We%20need%20a%20parliamentarian%20who%20can%20speak%20for%20Assam's%20problems.%20Gaurav%20is%20a%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20Gandhi%20family.%20He%20has%20not%20spoken%20a%20single%20word%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Assam%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sarma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20said%20that%20he%20is%20inspired%20if%20someone%20speaks%20for%20Assam%20inside%20Parliament%20since%20that%20helps%20expediting%20any%20pending%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20(Gaurav%20Gogoi)%20only%20speaks%20about%20Manipur%20in%20Parliament.%20Is%20he%20a%20son-in-law%20or%20grandchild%20of%20Manipur%3F%20Why%20does%20he%20speak%20about%20Manipur%20day%20and%20night%3F%20And%20some%20people%20here%20are%20enthused%20that%20he%20spoke%20a%20lot%20in%20Parliament.%20Assam%20remained%20backward%20for%20such%20statements%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713284760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F965ud9io_himanta-sarma_625x300_06_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-wants-to-look-at-amul-babies-himanta-sarma-jibe-at-priyanka-gandhi-vadra-5456438%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hours%20after%20Congress%20leader%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20led%20a%20roadshow%20in%20Assam's%20Jo