00w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-5-1713159172-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-5-1713159172-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-5-1713159172-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347264%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKinara%20Capital%20has%20disbursed%20over%201.2%20lakh%20loans%20so%20far%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20major%20credit%20gap%2C%20the%20consultant%20found%2C%20was%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98missing%20middle%E2%80%99%2C%20of%20people%20in%20need%20of%20loans%20in%20the%20range%20of%20Rs%201%20lakh%20to%20Rs%2010%20lakh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeeting%20these%20small%20business%20owners%2C%20SHGs%2C%20women%20entrepreneurs%2C%20led%20to%20a%20deja%20vu%20moment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDidn%E2%80%99t%20her%20mother%20face%20the%20same%20problem%2025%20years%20back%3F%20Why%20was%20no%20one%20able%20to%20fix%20this%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325587%2Fmumbai-entrepreneur-runs-lending-platform-for-rural-indian-women-loans-businesses%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecredit%20gap%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20this%20income%20group%2C%20wondered%20Hardika.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetermined%20to%20ensure%20that%20no%20one%20should%20have%20unfulfilled%20dreams%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20capital%20like%20her%20mother%2C%20the%2053-year-old%20decided%20to%20solve%20the%20problem.%20Providing%20collateral%20was%20a%20major%20problem%20in%20this%20bracket%2C%20which%20she%20solved%20through%20Kinara%20Capital%20by%20providing%20unsecured%20loans.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20biggest%20gap%20across%20tier%201%2C%202%20and%203%20cities%20was%20unsecured%20business%20lending%2C%20as%20most%20of%20the%20borrowers%20