a.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fkanthari-3_11zon-1711979994-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346185%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAt%20kanthari%20the%20changemakers%20are%20mentored%20by%20%E2%80%98catalysts%E2%80%99%20who%20give%20them%20guidance%20with%20respect%20to%20the%20nuances%20of%20running%20a%20business%20and%20pitching%20to%20investors%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Sabriye%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20that%20was%20the%20day%2C%20her%20perspective%20shifted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20during%20her%20higher%20secondary%20education%20at%20a%20school%20for%20the%20blind%20in%20Germany%2C%20that%20Sabriye%20learnt%20how%20a%20disability%20does%20not%20need%20to%20be%20equivalent%20to%20being%20put%20in%20a%20drawer%20by%20society%20and%20made%20claustrophobic.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20my%20new%20school%2C%20I%20was%20introduced%20to%20skiing%2C%20horse%20riding%2C%20acrobatics%2C%20windsurfing%2C%20and%20kayaking.%20I%20began%20to%20fall%20in%20love%20with%20these%20activities%20and%20become%20more%20confident.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESabriye%20went%20on%20to%20pursue%20Tibetology%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Bonn%2C%20and%20it%20was%20during%20these%20years%20that%20she%20developed%20the%20Tibetan%20braille%20script%20combining%20the%20principles%20of%20the%20braille%20system%20with%20the%20special%20features%20of%20the%20Tibetan%20syllable-based%20script.%20Once%20examined%20by%20Tibetan%20scholars%20who%20deemed%20it%20easily%20understandable%2C%20the%20script%20became%20the%20officially%20recognised%20one%20in%20braille%20literature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20her%20education%2C%20Sabriye%20decided%20to%20pursue%20her%20dream%20of%20working%20with%20an%20international%20humanitarian%20network%20that%20works%20to%20save%20lives%20and%20build%20community%20resilience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20I%20was%20asked%20of%20what%20use%20would%20I%20be%20on%20the%20ground%20since%20I%20was%20blind.%20So%2C%20I%20decided%20if%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20a%20part%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F161743%2Fsst-tamil-nadu-farmers-organic-farming%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20organisation%20creating%20change%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20would%20start%20one%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20kanthari%20is%20the%20realisation%20of%20that%20dream.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELeaders%20without%20boundaries%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20people%20of%20rural%20India%20have%20aspirations%2C%20what%20is%20missing%20are%20organisations%20that%20can%20turn%20these%20into%20a%20reality.%20This%20was%20what%20Sabriye%20and%20her%20Dutch%20engineer%20partner%20Paul%20Kronenberg%20%E2%80%94%20whom%20she%20met%20during%20her%20trip%20to%20Tibet%20in%201997%20%E2%80%94%20discovered%20while%20they%20were%20researching%20existing%20entrepreneurship%20courses%20in%20India%20in%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20courses%20necessitated%20degrees.%20But%20as%20I%20see%20it%2C%20all%20one%20must%20have%20to%20start%20something%20is%20a%20dream.%20Degrees%20come%20second%2C%E2%80%9D%20emphasises%20Sabriye.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%2C%20thus%20set%20out%20to%20launch%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334155%2Fbengaluru-ngo-dream-a-dream-educates-underprivileged-children-life-skills-happiness-curriculum-delhi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20social%20endeavour%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20anyone%20who%20had%20the%20%E2%80%9Cguts%20to%20challenge%20the%20status%20quo%20and%20create%20something%20meaningful%20to%20make%20the%20world%20a%20better%20place%E2%80%9D%20would%20be%20trained%20and%20equipped%20with%20the%20necessary%20resources.%20The%20place%20of%20choice%20was%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20Thiruvananthapu