%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-21-1712904349-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-21-1712904349-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347146%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EOrchids%20at%20Greens%20and%20Blooms%20Nursery%20in%20Pune%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20learnt%20a%20lot%20from%20my%20father.%20I%20would%20follow%20him%20everywhere%20and%20much%20of%20my%20knowledge%20and%20working%20style%20comes%20from%20watching%20him.%20I%20wanted%20to%20take%20his%20name%20forward%20and%20chose%20to%20study%20BSc%20agriculture%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bhausaheb%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20his%20education%20in%20Pune%2C%20he%20worked%20in%20polyhouses%20and%20horticulture%20training%20centres.%20He%20was%20one%20of%20the%20early%20adopters%20when%20the%20floriculture%20industry%20started%20in%20India.%20After%20his%20stints%20in%20the%20country%2C%20he%20worked%20in%20Ethiopia%20for%2010%20years%20where%20he%20handled%20over%20200%20acres%20of%20rose%20cultivation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20returning%20to%20India%20in%202015%2C%20while%20he%20wanted%20to%20start%20his%20business%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20work%20in%20a%20nursery%20in%20Pune%20to%20understand%20the%20Indian%20market%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201360px)%20100vw%2C%201360px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIMG20200821110333-min-1712904916.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221360%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Different%20types%20of%20exotic%20flowers%20are%20grown%20at%20Greens%20and%20Blooms%20nursery%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIMG20200821110333-min-1712904916.jpg%201360w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2