%20will%20help.%20My%20mother%20believes%20that%20medicines%20treat%20your%20body%20but%20books%20heal%20your%20soul%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20eatery%20has%20also%20since%20kept%20on%20growing%20and%20people%20have%20donated%20books%20to%20Aaji%E2%80%99s%20collection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20expresses%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20feel%20delighted%20when%20I%20see%20people%20reading%20books%20at%20the%20eatery.%20All%20my%20life%2C%20I%20have%20struggled%20to%20have%20a%20stable%20life%2C%20but%20what%20kept%20me%20going%20was%20my%20children.%20For%20a%20woman%20who%20was%20always%20fond%20of%20reading%20but%20never%20got%20to%2C%20when%20I%20see%20young%20children%20come%20to%20the%20eatery%20and%20read%2C%20I%20feel%20like%20I%20have%20succeeded%20in%20my%20initiative%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20have%20spare%20books%20that%20you%20want%20to%20donate%20to%20the%20eatery%2C%20you%20can%20reach%20out%20to%20Pravin%20at%209922946622%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20pictures%20credit%3A%20Pravin)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712827324000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-1-1710406948.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D344848%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nashik's%20Bhimabai%20Jondhale%20always%20loved%20reading%20but%20never%20got%20a%20chance%20to%20tend%20to%20her%20passion.%20Today%2C%20she%20runs%20'Ajjichya%20Pustakancha%20Hotel'%2C%20a%20unique%20book%20hotel%20which%20serves%20delicious%20meals%20along%20with%20free%20books%20to%20read!%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344848%2Fnashik-bhimabai-jondhale-ajjichya-pustakancha-hotel-book-hotel-by-grandmother%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Miles%20To%2